# Key Findings

## 1: Educational Content Wins
- Buyers prefer educational content over promotional content.
- Long-form content builds trust.

## 2: Distribution Matters More Than Creation
- Content distribution is becoming more important than content production.
- Repurposing increases ROI.

## 3: Theme 3: AI Is Changing Discovery
- AI search, YouTube, Reddit, and communities are becoming major discovery channels.
- Trust and expertise matter more than ever.